==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Desynonymize
<hw>De`syn*on"y*mize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To deprive
of synonymous character; to discriminate in use; -- applied to words
which have been employed as synonyms.</def> <rj><au>Coleridge.
Trench.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Detach</ent>⟦br⟧
